Salt optional.analyse
====================

Pillar example::

matomo:
  install_dir: /var/www/matomo
  domain: analytics.example.com
  php_fpm_socket: /run/php/php8.3-fpm.sock
  owner: www-data
  group: www-data
  db:
    enabled: true
    provider: existing   # existing | mariadb
    name: matomo
    user: matomo
    password: changeme
    host: localhost
    socket: /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock
    admin_user: root
    admin_password: ''   # 默认读取全局 mysql_password，如保留空值
